comments.body:
I created a  sample project using Titanium SDK 3.2.3 GA + Titanium CLI 3.2.3 + Titanium Studio 3.2.3 and was able to launch it without any error on iPhone Retina (4 inch 64-bit) simulator. 

What version of Xcode and iOS SDK you are using?

Please attach the output of the following command to investigate further.

ti info -t iOS
Resolving this ticket as I cannot reproduce this issue and the reporter has not provided requested information.
